      ** LEFECALAV Parameters
     D FELPDT          S              5  0
     D FELADT          S              5  0
     D FEPSTD          S              5  0
     D FEPEND          S              5  0
     D FECALT          S              2
     D FECALC          S              1  0
     D FEPIND          S              1
     D FEFCCY          S              3
     D FEERAT          S             13  8
     D FEMDIN          S              1
     D FEINDC          S              1                                                     MD061267

      ** Working variables
     D ZFLD15          S             15  0
     D ZDECS           S              1  0
     D ZECODE          S              1
